CUNY DATA 602 Advanced Programming Techniques
Assignment #2
Web Trader App


The first 4 functions of this app create the main menu and 3 pages that you can navigate to from the main menu.
show_main_page
show_trade_screen
show_blotter
show_pl

The next 2 functions create some analytics and charts on the comfirm transaction page and execute the transaction.
confirmation
execute_trade

These 2 functions create the charts that are displayed on the confirm transaction page.
chart_avgprice_90days
chart_price_100trades

These 3 retrieve and parse html data.
get_last_100_trades
get_90_day_history
get_quote

These next 3 retrieve information from the MongoDB.
get_portfolio
get_pl_row
get_position

The final 4 functions handle exceptions and provide hyperlinks to the other menu pages.
invalid_input
no_money_left
no_units_to_sell
retrieval_failure

